title: Will we ever get Dominion
body: Is there any point in the foreseeable that oce will get Dominion, do we have the population for it and is the league community growing to the point where we will?

replies.body: Join the chat room Dominion, not many people are on it but sometimes people set up Dominion games

From memory the last change they made to available queues was to remove Team Builder because there weren't enough people. Given that direction I'd say if you want matchmade Dominion (or more of any queue we don't have) you should be moving to NA.
I have asked this question countless times in community and to developers but it seems not in near future since the answer i got was we are not sure OCE players would like a game mode like dominion
